verbose_text: alpha-Syn-induced chemotaxis failure shown in the present studies may not be artefactual effects caused by a denatured protein expressed in E. coli but may represent a bona fide nature of this protein since alpha-Syn purified from human erythrocytes caused similar inhibitory effects on cell migration (XREF_FIG).
evidence: alpha-Syn purified from human erythrocytes caused similar inhibitory effects on cell migration
